trans-unit.source: For more information, see the topic [Schema-ID-GUID](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_schemaidguid.asp) in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchemaProperty.SchemaGuid%2A> is used in many Active Directory Domain Services configuration operations, such as managing extended rights.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchemaProperty.SchemaGuid%2A>用于多个 Active Directory 域服务配置操作，如管理扩展的权限。
